OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781700487
OL,3,CEngland star Tino Livramento ruled out
OL,4,Cof World Cup due to injury
OL,6,FEngland full-back Tino Livramento has
OL,7,Fbeen ruled out of the World Cup due to
OL,8,Finjury.
OL,10,FThe Newcastle defender, 23, injured
OL,11,Fhis calf while training with the rest
OL,12,Fof the England squad at their Kansas
OL,13,FCity base on Sunday afternoon.
OL,15,FHe then underwent a scan and medical
OL,16,Fassessment on Monday, which confirmed
OL,17,Fhe could not play in the tournament,
OL,18,Fthe Football Association said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
