OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FChelsea centre-back Trevoh Chalobah
OL,12,Fhas now been drafted in as his
OL,13,Freplacement as the team prepares to
OL,14,Fplay Croatia on Wednesday evening in
OL,15,Ftheir World Cup opener.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
