OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781700487
OL,3,CEngland star Tino Livramento ruled out
OL,4,Cof World Cup due to injury
OL,6,F"Trevoh Chalobah has been called into
OL,7,FEngland's 26-player squad at Fifa
OL,8,FWorld Cup 2026 after injury sadly
OL,9,Fforced the withdrawal of Tino
OL,10,FLivramento," an England team statement
OL,11,Fread.
OL,13,F"Arrangements are now being made for
OL,14,Fthe Chelsea defender to make the
OL,15,Fjourney to the team's base camp in
OL,16,FKansas City, while the rest of the
OL,17,Fsquad will head to Dallas, Texas, for
OL,18,Fthe Three Lions' opening group fixture
OL,19,Fagainst Croatia on Wednesday."
