OL,3,CEngland star Tino Livramento ruled out
OL,4,Cof World Cup due to injury
OL,6,FFifa regulations allow teams to
OL,7,Freplace injured outfield players up
OL,8,Funtil 24 hours before their opening
OL,9,Fmatch.
OL,11,FTuchel had decided to select
OL,12,FLivramento for the World Cup despite
OL,13,Fthe full-back missing the end of an
OL,14,Finjury-disrupted season with a thigh
OL,15,Fissue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
