OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781700487
OL,3,CEngland star Tino Livramento ruled out
OL,4,Cof World Cup due to injury
OL,6,FThe six-cap defender has not played
OL,7,Ffor Newcastle since April 18, when the
OL,8,Fside was beaten by Bournemouth, and
OL,9,Fonly featured in one of England's warm-
OL,10,Fup friendlies in Florida, playing 45
OL,11,Fminutes off the bench against New
OL,12,FZealand.
OL,14,FChalobah only has one cap to his name,
OL,15,Fhaving started in last summer's
OL,16,Ffriendly against Senegal, where
OL,17,FEngland lost 3-1.
OL,19,FAlso in England's World Cup defence
OL,20,Fare Nico O'Reilly, Djed Spence, Reece
OL,21,FJames, Ezri Konsa, and Jarell Quansah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
