OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781700487
OL,3,CEngland star Tino Livramento ruled out
OL,4,Cof World Cup due to injury
OL,6,FManager Thomas Tuchel will announce
OL,7,FEngland's starting line-up for their
OL,8,Ffirst tournament match on Wednesday,
OL,9,Fwith the game due to kick-off at 3pm
OL,10,Flocal time and 9pm BST.
OL,12,FClose friends Jude Bellingham and
OL,13,FMorgan Rogers are one of the major
OL,14,Ftalking points of the team, as they
OL,15,Fare both competing to start as number
OL,16,F10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
